1
00:00:09,009 --> 00:00:11,053
The Battle of Synergy.

2
00:00:11,803 --> 00:00:15,515
Let's bring in
the second Revived Fate Reader.

3
00:00:18,143 --> 00:00:20,479
- Oh, gosh.
- Who is it?

4
00:00:20,562 --> 00:00:22,105
Who could it be?

5
00:00:22,689 --> 00:00:24,525
Welcome back.

6
00:00:24,608 --> 00:00:25,859
- Who is it?
- I'm anxious.

7
00:00:25,943 --> 00:00:27,527
- Who?
- Welcome back.

8
00:00:29,529 --> 00:00:30,614
Who?

9
00:00:30,697 --> 00:00:32,366
What?

10
00:00:32,449 --> 00:00:34,284
- This person was so close.
- Noh Seulbi.

11
00:00:34,368 --> 00:00:35,744
- Yes.
- She's good.

12
00:00:35,827 --> 00:00:37,287
She made an impression too.

13
00:00:37,371 --> 00:00:39,081
- She guessed well too.
- Yes.

14
00:00:39,164 --> 00:00:42,459
- I want to bring back this person.
- Yes.

15
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:46,880
I can see there have been a lot
of shamans in your family for generations.

16
00:00:49,216 --> 00:00:50,217
Family of shamans. She's right.

17
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:52,386
I'm getting goosebumps already.

18
00:00:52,469 --> 00:00:54,263
You were at death's door.

19
00:00:54,346 --> 00:00:56,640
Your fate changed drastically
when you were 5.

20
00:00:56,723 --> 00:01:00,644
He got famous
as the possessed kid when he was 5.

21
00:01:00,727 --> 00:01:02,187
Almost died.

22
00:01:02,271 --> 00:01:03,397
ALMOST DIED REFUSING THE CALLING

23
00:01:09,987 --> 00:01:11,989
Oh, what?

24
00:01:12,614 --> 00:01:14,074
It's Seulbi.

25
00:01:14,658 --> 00:01:16,952
- It's Seulbi.
- Seulbi?

26
00:01:17,035 --> 00:01:19,246
I was shocked.

27
00:01:19,329 --> 00:01:20,956
- Wow!
- Wow.

28
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:24,084
Wait, she's back? Are you serious?

29
00:01:24,668 --> 00:01:26,420
Totally unexpected.

30
00:01:28,338 --> 00:01:31,258
I got the chills
when Seulbi walked in.

31
00:01:33,176 --> 00:01:35,262
I've been given a second chance.

32
00:01:35,762 --> 00:01:37,931
My Granny spirit and I are determined.

33
00:01:38,682 --> 00:01:41,476
Young Master Plum Blossom
and Noh Seulbi

34
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:45,689
are back in the Battle of Fates.

35
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:48,025
Huge congratulations.

36
00:01:48,108 --> 00:01:50,902
- Good to have you back.
- Welcome to the den of evil.

37
00:01:53,071 --> 00:01:55,824
He said "the den of evil."

38
00:01:56,825 --> 00:01:57,951
There's tension.

39
00:01:58,035 --> 00:02:00,704
The air has changed.

40
00:02:01,288 --> 00:02:05,042
Well, I sort of clashed with Seulbi,

41
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:06,877
so I had mixed feelings.

42
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:07,961
Now…

43
00:02:09,254 --> 00:02:11,506
…we will start forming the teams.

44
00:02:12,549 --> 00:02:13,675
The 4 teams are

45
00:02:14,843 --> 00:02:15,886
Cheongryong,

46
00:02:15,969 --> 00:02:17,012
Baekho,

47
00:02:17,095 --> 00:02:18,138
Jujak,

48
00:02:18,221 --> 00:02:20,349
and Hyeonmu.

49
00:02:20,891 --> 00:02:23,477
They represent the Azure Dragon,

50
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:25,270
the White Tiger,

51
00:02:25,354 --> 00:02:26,688
the Vermilion Bird,

52
00:02:26,772 --> 00:02:29,816
and the Black Tortoise,
all of which are sacred beasts.

53
00:02:30,734 --> 00:02:34,112
They are known as the 4 Gods,

54
00:02:34,196 --> 00:02:37,074
the guardians
of the 4 cardinal directions.

55
00:02:39,701 --> 00:02:42,621
I hope to team up with someone
my deities get on with.

56
00:02:42,704 --> 00:02:44,206
Please. How will they form the teams?

57
00:02:46,249 --> 00:02:48,126
Dear 12 Fate Readers.

58
00:02:48,877 --> 00:02:51,630
Form your teams as you wish.

59
00:02:52,381 --> 00:02:53,715
No way.

60
00:02:56,301 --> 00:02:58,178
We can decide on our own?

61
00:02:59,763 --> 00:03:00,889
What do I do?

62
00:03:00,972 --> 00:03:02,474
Who should I team up with?

63
00:03:02,974 --> 00:03:04,559
I'm sure they know…

64
00:03:04,643 --> 00:03:05,644
Which combo would be best.

65
00:03:05,727 --> 00:03:07,688
They'll see who'd be good teammates.

66
00:03:08,438 --> 00:03:09,898
What would be the good combo?

67
00:03:09,981 --> 00:03:11,566
Should the shamans stick together?

68
00:03:11,650 --> 00:03:13,068
But I think they'll end up arguing.

69
00:03:13,151 --> 00:03:15,195
I'm sure there will be diverse mixes.

70
00:03:19,866 --> 00:03:21,451
I want to team up with you, ma'am.

71
00:03:21,535 --> 00:03:22,661
Oh, thank you.

72
00:03:23,203 --> 00:03:24,413
Oh, thank you.

73
00:03:24,913 --> 00:03:27,499
- If we win, we'll advance together.
- That's right.

74
00:03:27,582 --> 00:03:30,877
I was determined to
team up with Monad.

75
00:03:30,961 --> 00:03:34,339
She's a tarot master,
and her readings were so accurate.

76
00:03:34,423 --> 00:03:38,802
The moment I heard "homeless,"
the first thing I thought was "no home."

77
00:03:38,885 --> 00:03:40,387
Homeless people have no homes.

78
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:43,598
However, for number 4,
the card suggests they're without a home.

79
00:03:43,682 --> 00:03:46,268
- How do you get that with tarot?
- How did she get that?

80
00:03:46,351 --> 00:03:49,771
I picked out some cards,
and there are no negative cards

81
00:03:49,855 --> 00:03:52,399
between the man and the woman.

82
00:03:52,482 --> 00:03:54,443
I don't think they broke up
because they wanted to.

83
00:03:54,526 --> 00:03:56,778
I think there was some sort of condition.

84
00:03:58,029 --> 00:03:59,156
Goodness.

85
00:03:59,239 --> 00:04:01,199
That was so accurate.

86
00:04:01,283 --> 00:04:03,285
I thought we'd be a good fit
for each other,

87
00:04:03,368 --> 00:04:05,996
so I chose Monad.

88
00:04:06,079 --> 00:04:08,248
Which room should we go to?

89
00:04:08,331 --> 00:04:11,168
- How about the red one?
- Red sounds good.

90
00:04:11,751 --> 00:04:13,920
A RED FLAG SIGNALS AFFIRMATION

91
00:04:14,004 --> 00:04:16,047
-Shall we go take a seat?
-Sure, let's.

92
00:04:16,131 --> 00:04:17,841
- Yeah?
- Shall we do that?

93
00:04:17,924 --> 00:04:19,843
- Whatever. Let's sit down.
- Let's sit.

94
00:04:21,136 --> 00:04:22,262
All right.

95
00:04:22,345 --> 00:04:24,765
- You were my top pick.
- Thank you.

96
00:04:27,309 --> 00:04:28,435
Where should I go?

97
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,145
Come join us.

98
00:04:30,228 --> 00:04:31,354
Come join us.

99
00:04:31,438 --> 00:04:32,939
Come on. Welcome.

100
00:04:33,565 --> 00:04:35,358
The obanggi say,
"It's a green light!"

101
00:04:35,442 --> 00:04:36,735
- All right.
- Green light!

102
00:04:36,818 --> 00:04:37,819
It's perfect.

103
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:41,198
Kwon Sujin is a manshin.

104
00:04:41,281 --> 00:04:44,534
She must have know-how and lots of data.

105
00:04:44,618 --> 00:04:49,164
- I didn't hesitate to ask her to join us.
- Let's do it together.

106
00:04:49,247 --> 00:04:52,417
- They've teamed up already?
- For real?

107
00:04:52,501 --> 00:04:53,752
This fast?

108
00:04:54,586 --> 00:04:57,255
- This is great.
- Luck is on our side.

109
00:04:57,339 --> 00:04:58,340
Let's do this!

110
00:04:58,423 --> 00:05:01,885
Oh, dear.
Where should I go?

111
00:05:03,762 --> 00:05:05,639
-Lady Wish?
-Yes?

112
00:05:05,722 --> 00:05:07,974
- Shall we go together?
- Shall we?

113
00:05:08,058 --> 00:05:10,560
-Which room would you like?
-The red one's already taken.

114
00:05:10,644 --> 00:05:12,646
In the second round,

115
00:05:12,729 --> 00:05:17,484
my deity and Lady Wish
seemed to get along well.

116
00:05:17,567 --> 00:05:21,279
I thought our readings would be similar

117
00:05:21,363 --> 00:05:24,825
and that we'd have
a similar approach to the questions.

118
00:05:24,908 --> 00:05:27,410
That's why I went to her first.

119
00:05:27,494 --> 00:05:28,912
- How about green?
- Sure, sounds good.

120
00:05:28,995 --> 00:05:30,413
Looks good to me.

121
00:05:30,497 --> 00:05:32,332
Since we're both shamans,

122
00:05:32,415 --> 00:05:35,585
I thought we'd need a myungri
expert.

123
00:05:35,669 --> 00:05:39,714
So I was hoping Pie would join us,

124
00:05:39,798 --> 00:05:41,174
but I wasn't sure if he would.

125
00:05:43,552 --> 00:05:45,512
Pie! Welcome.

126
00:05:45,595 --> 00:05:47,848
- Join us, Pie.
- Let's do this together.

127
00:05:47,931 --> 00:05:49,099
Welcome. Have a seat.

128
00:05:49,182 --> 00:05:51,351
I was so happy to team up with them.

129
00:05:51,434 --> 00:05:54,187
I think that team will be
quiet but powerful.

130
00:05:54,271 --> 00:05:55,522
Looks like a strong team.

131
00:05:55,605 --> 00:05:56,648
I love our energy.

132
00:05:56,731 --> 00:05:57,858
LADY WISH, PIE,
YOUNG MASTER PLUM BLOSSOM

133
00:05:58,817 --> 00:06:00,569
This is so hard.

134
00:06:04,155 --> 00:06:08,952
I am pretty timid and shy.

135
00:06:09,035 --> 00:06:11,746
I didn't like 1 of them,

136
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:14,583
so I assumed there would be Fate Readers

137
00:06:14,666 --> 00:06:16,501
who didn't like me.

138
00:06:17,002 --> 00:06:18,837
So I decided to trust in my Granny spirit

139
00:06:19,838 --> 00:06:21,923
and went to where she told me to go.

140
00:06:22,924 --> 00:06:23,925
The White Tiger room.

141
00:06:26,428 --> 00:06:27,762
-Then I'll…
-Where should we go?

142
00:06:28,805 --> 00:06:30,140
I want to go to that room.

143
00:06:31,308 --> 00:06:33,768
I went to the yellow room because "yellow"
in Korean sounds like my surname.

144
00:06:34,686 --> 00:06:36,646
My birth chart has 6 Earth elements,

145
00:06:36,730 --> 00:06:38,064
which are signified by yellow.

146
00:06:38,148 --> 00:06:39,816
And I was born
on the day of the Yellow Snake.

147
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:41,318
So I thought it was fate.

148
00:06:41,401 --> 00:06:43,653
I went for the yellow room.
I just liked it.

149
00:06:43,737 --> 00:06:45,030
I want to go to that room.

150
00:06:45,113 --> 00:06:46,740
So I walked over,

151
00:06:46,823 --> 00:06:48,742
but Jiseon beat me to it.

152
00:06:49,451 --> 00:06:51,369
I'll be sitting in this room.

153
00:06:51,453 --> 00:06:52,454
But what can I do?

154
00:06:52,537 --> 00:06:54,748
Yellow is my energy,
so I just went for it.

155
00:07:00,211 --> 00:07:02,881
Wait, what? She's teaming up
with Young Master Jiseon?

156
00:07:02,964 --> 00:07:05,508
What? Young Master Jiseon
and Noh Seulbi teamed up!

157
00:07:05,592 --> 00:07:07,719
- Young Master Jiseon?
- Those 2 together?

158
00:07:07,802 --> 00:07:09,596
- For real?
- Yes!

159
00:07:11,181 --> 00:07:13,266
- Do you like this room too?
- Yes.

160
00:07:17,479 --> 00:07:20,690
I didn't want to team up with Noh Seulbi.

161
00:07:20,774 --> 00:07:23,526
She was my rival.

162
00:07:23,610 --> 00:07:24,611
Kiddo.

163
00:07:24,694 --> 00:07:26,029
All right, little boy?

164
00:07:26,112 --> 00:07:27,155
Are you crying?

165
00:07:28,615 --> 00:07:29,908
Don't belittle others.

166
00:07:33,036 --> 00:07:34,954
Ah, this is bad.

167
00:07:35,038 --> 00:07:36,998
Out of the frying pan into the fire.

168
00:07:38,541 --> 00:07:39,542
Where should I go?

169
00:07:40,168 --> 00:07:41,169
One, two.

170
00:07:47,717 --> 00:07:49,135
Oh, geez!

171
00:07:49,219 --> 00:07:50,720
Why would Mr. Kim join them?

172
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:54,099
I do both foot reading and saju.

173
00:07:54,432 --> 00:07:56,351
I joined them

174
00:07:56,434 --> 00:07:59,562
because I thought the 2 shamans
and I would create great synergy.

175
00:08:00,105 --> 00:08:01,439
This is shocking.

176
00:08:01,523 --> 00:08:04,943
-Jiseon's the youngest, so the age gap…
-You're right.

177
00:08:05,026 --> 00:08:07,070
- It's huge.
- Well, it's a done deal.

178
00:08:07,153 --> 00:08:08,363
I'll sit in the middle.

179
00:08:09,614 --> 00:08:13,034
We must strategize.

180
00:08:13,118 --> 00:08:15,036
Okay? We need a strategy.

181
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:17,622
Let's strategize together.

182
00:08:17,706 --> 00:08:19,624
KIM BAEKMUN, NOH SEULBI,
YOUNG MASTER JISEON

183
00:08:23,002 --> 00:08:24,963
Oh, wait.

184
00:08:25,755 --> 00:08:27,090
What should we do?

185
00:08:27,632 --> 00:08:29,509
I like Hannah so much.

186
00:08:29,592 --> 00:08:33,513
She's polite, and her readings are neat.

187
00:08:33,596 --> 00:08:37,434
And Seolhwa has the boldness
of a novice shaman,

188
00:08:37,517 --> 00:08:39,227
and I love that.

189
00:08:42,439 --> 00:08:44,482
Where will you go?

190
00:08:45,525 --> 00:08:49,487
Two shamans and a spiritual tarot master.

191
00:08:49,571 --> 00:08:51,865
We're basically the Avengers.

192
00:08:52,198 --> 00:08:53,992
- I was drawn to the blue.
- Shall we sit here?

193
00:08:54,075 --> 00:08:56,369
Blue helps with concentration.

194
00:08:56,453 --> 00:08:58,204
Team Azure Dragon seems strong too.

195
00:08:58,288 --> 00:09:00,081
They're formidable for sure.

196
00:09:00,165 --> 00:09:02,417
Let's do this!

197
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:03,710
SEOLHWA,
LEE SOBIN, CHOI HANNAH

198
00:09:03,793 --> 00:09:05,211
Ladies, I love you.

199
00:09:05,712 --> 00:09:07,589
- I love you, ladies.
- We're a team now.

200
00:09:07,672 --> 00:09:09,549
We're in this together.
Let's make it to the next round.

201
00:09:09,632 --> 00:09:11,092
Let's do this together.

202
00:09:12,343 --> 00:09:13,845
The Battle of Synergy.

203
00:09:13,928 --> 00:09:16,723
The 4 teams have been formed.

204
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:18,683
Team Azure Dragon.

205
00:09:19,309 --> 00:09:20,310
Team White Tiger.

206
00:09:21,061 --> 00:09:22,353
Team Vermilion Bird.

207
00:09:22,437 --> 00:09:23,897
Team Black Tortoise.

208
00:09:25,523 --> 00:09:30,028
The number of survivors
in the Battle of Synergy is

209
00:09:31,321 --> 00:09:32,447
6.

210
00:09:34,199 --> 00:09:36,034
Half will go.

211
00:09:36,117 --> 00:09:38,787
Another half will be gone.

212
00:09:39,871 --> 00:09:41,331
The Battle of Synergy

213
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:45,085
consists of 2 matches.

214
00:09:45,168 --> 00:09:48,338
In the first match,
1 of the 4 teams will survive.

215
00:09:49,047 --> 00:09:51,007
In the second match,

216
00:09:51,091 --> 00:09:54,094
1 of the 3 remaining teams will survive.

217
00:09:55,136 --> 00:09:57,138
Two matches?

218
00:09:58,098 --> 00:10:01,351
- We must win the first one no matter what.
- Yeah, we have to.

219
00:10:01,434 --> 00:10:06,397
We will now reveal the fate
for you to read.

220
00:10:11,111 --> 00:10:13,571
I wondered what kind of
team mission they would've prepared.

221
00:10:13,655 --> 00:10:16,282
What could it be?
What kind of question would they give us?

222
00:10:16,366 --> 00:10:19,410
I was confident
I could take on any kind of question.

223
00:10:19,494 --> 00:10:20,912
Let's win this, no matter what.

224
00:10:28,086 --> 00:10:29,087
Whoa.

225
00:10:34,050 --> 00:10:36,261
- Someone's coming out.
- Yeah, looks like it.

226
00:10:39,264 --> 00:10:40,473
It's about a person?

227
00:10:45,812 --> 00:10:48,731
It looks like they're
carrying something. What are those?

228
00:10:48,815 --> 00:10:51,025
It looks like a briefcase
from a James Bond movie.

229
00:10:51,651 --> 00:10:54,696
We've got men and women
with identical briefcases.

230
00:10:56,531 --> 00:10:59,325
My gosh. There are a lot of them.

231
00:10:59,409 --> 00:11:00,743
Whoa, so many.

232
00:11:01,411 --> 00:11:02,537
Oh, my gosh.

233
00:11:03,872 --> 00:11:05,373
Why are there so many people?

234
00:11:07,167 --> 00:11:08,293
Whoa.

235
00:11:15,341 --> 00:11:16,426
What a sight.

236
00:11:22,265 --> 00:11:23,308
What is this?

237
00:11:24,225 --> 00:11:25,685
It looks like their age

238
00:11:25,768 --> 00:11:27,979
ranges from 30s to maybe 50s, right?

239
00:11:28,062 --> 00:11:30,982
Mmm. They're on the older side.

240
00:11:37,614 --> 00:11:39,282
Standing before you

241
00:11:40,074 --> 00:11:43,077
are 11 men and women.

242
00:11:45,955 --> 00:11:48,082
Five of them

243
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:52,212
are wealthy individuals with assets
of over 10 billion won.

244
00:11:56,758 --> 00:11:57,800
Ten billion won?

245
00:11:59,385 --> 00:12:00,720
Over 10 billion?

246
00:12:01,888 --> 00:12:02,931
I'm jealous!

247
00:12:06,059 --> 00:12:09,062
Read the energy of wealth
and money in their fates

248
00:12:10,271 --> 00:12:12,815
and find the billionaires.

249
00:12:13,942 --> 00:12:16,486
That's impossible.

250
00:12:18,404 --> 00:12:20,114
You can't tell
just by looking at their faces.

251
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:26,204
They were right in front of us,

252
00:12:26,287 --> 00:12:30,208
and I wanted to see their faces
and feel their energy.

253
00:12:30,291 --> 00:12:34,420
And at that moment, weirdly,
I sensed a windfall.

254
00:12:34,963 --> 00:12:37,173
I could see it.

255
00:12:37,715 --> 00:12:40,760
I just listened to
my Granny spirit and followed my gut.

256
00:12:41,261 --> 00:12:43,388
I'm 100% sure about the guy in green.

257
00:12:44,264 --> 00:12:46,808
Not 10 billion in cash,
but he also has properties.

258
00:12:46,891 --> 00:12:48,268
The one in the green sweater.

259
00:12:49,727 --> 00:12:51,896
I wanted to check,

260
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:53,523
so I drew the obanggi.

261
00:12:53,606 --> 00:12:54,816
Oh, good.

262
00:12:54,899 --> 00:12:57,944
I got a red flag,
so I knew we'd make it through.

263
